FBIS3-30753 "dreeu026_p_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-026 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Feb 1994 POLAND Prime Minister Accepts Borowski's Resignation LD0802105394 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1036 GMT 8 Feb 94 LD0802105394 Warsaw PAP Language: Polish Article Type:BFN [Text] Warsaw, 8 Feb--Prime Minister Waldemar Pawlak has accepted the resignation of Marek Borowski, deputy prime minister and finance minister. The head of the government informed journalists of his decision this morning before a meeting of the government. Marek Borowski is taking part in the government meeting.
